    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372850/extras/45d84b187f7861deb3a541a5154becb9.avif?t=1680032675\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>Spring is coming to your bakery! Celebrate all the new-ness of spring with a fun mix of Easter items too! Hang up pastel banners, and pretty floral cutouts around your bakery. Bake bunny cakes, and bumble bee cookies all the while keeping on the lookout for decorated eggs hidden around your bakery!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372850/extras/fdfa6375d3dceed41d7364813cf027e6.avif?t=1680032675\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>Get your bakery fresh and ready for Spring with a fun mix of decorations! String up pretty bunting, hang butterfly banners, egg-cellent chalkboard designs, paper cutouts of flowers, bows, and more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372850/extras/5f43252085b56f1609214663c7c73990.avif?t=1680032675\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>We’ve added over 40 new Spring and Easter-themed recipes. Picture lots of flowers, bunnies, bumble bees, Easter eggs, and spring chicks all in the form of cakes, cookies, donuts, and more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372850/extras/aeaf148de26da5172545c56b0204c7d0.avif?t=1680032675\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>As you bake and sell festive recipes you'll earn 'Spring Tickets' that you can collect and spend in the Spring Shop.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372850/extras/2918278679b60b100bf862fbfcefe27e.avif?t=1680032675\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>Find decorated eggs hiding in random places inside and outside of your bakery. Collect them to earn extra Spring Tickets!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372850/extras/038ed8062bccb76f2f98cb9f85019d17.avif?t=1680032675\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>Spend your tickets in the spring shop to buy lovely decorations, potted flowers, wallpapers, and more!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372850/extras/afa81da359851222af55b42bad07ed66.avif?t=1680032675\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>Put out your favorite refillable candy basket for your customers to spread the springtime feeling!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372850/extras/4d9c6a8aa4280d145277f8065a57a57a.avif?t=1680032675\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>We've added 9 seasonal wallpapers including different flower wallpapers, Easter egg wallpapers, and fresh spring grid wallpapers.",
